Lieutenant-General Khin Nyunt, first secretary of the Myanmar
State Peace and Development Council, as well as Aung San Suu Kyi,
general secretary of the opposition National League for Democracy
(NLD).
</P>
<P>
The visit came over a month after the NLD formed on September
