signing of a ceasefire agreement by government and MILF peace
negotiators to stop the skirmishes in the complex, both camps also
traded mortar fires at each other.
</P>
<P>
Last week, the two sides engaged in a week-long gunbattle,
killing three government soldiers, 20 MILF rebels and wounding
dozens of combatants from both sides, according to the government
army. 
