<HEADLINE> Hong Kong Stocks Open Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, October 27 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong stocks dropped
34.48 points, or 0.35 percent, to open at 9,744.43 Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
The blue-chip Hang Seng Index fell 38.84 points, or 0.40
percent, to close at 9,778.91 Monday. 
</P>
